quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  42,20,"Ugamije gushaka ibihembo by’umunsi w’imperuka, tuzamwongerera ibihembo bye, n’ugamije gushaka ibihembo by’isi, tuzamuhaho ariko ku munsi w’imperuka nta mugabane azagira"
  42,21,"Ese (abahakanyi) baba bafite ibigirwamana byabashyiriyeho amategeko mu idini Allah atigeze ahera uburenganzira (abantu)? N’iyo bitaza kuba ijambo ryo kudahaniraho, bari gucirwaho iteka (ryo kurimbuka). Kandi mu by’ukuri, abahakanyi bazahanishwa ibihano bibabaza"
  42,22,"(Ku munsi w’imperuka) uzabona abahakanyi batewe ubwoba (n’ibihano) by’ibyo bakoze, kandi bigomba kubageraho nta kabuza. Nyamara babandi bemeye bakanakora ibikorwa byiza, bazaba bari mu busitani bwo mu ijuru, bahabwa ibyo bashatse kwa Nyagasani wabo. Izo ni zo ngabire z’ikirenga"
  42,23,"Iyo ni yo nkuru nziza Allah aha abagaragu be bemeye bakanakora ibikorwa byiza. Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti \"(Kubagezaho ubutumwa) simbibasabira igihembo (yemwe bantu ba Maka), usibye gusa urukundo rw’isano (mfitanye namwe). Kandi uzakora icyiza, tuzamutuburira (ibihembo) byacyo. Mu by’ukuri, Allah ni Ubabarira ibyaha, Ushima (ibikorwa by’abagaragu be)"
  42,24,"Bavuga ko (Muhamadi) yahimbiye Allah ikinyoma, ariko iyo Allah aza kubishaka yari kadanangira umutima wawe (iyo uramuka ubikoze). Kandi Allah akuraho ibitari ukuri agashimangiza ukuri amagambo ye. Mu by’ukuri, we ni Umumenyi uhebuje w’ibiri mu bituza (by’abantu)"
  42,25,"Ni nawe wakira ukwicuza kw’abagaragu be, akanababarira ibibi. Kandi azi neza ibyo mukora"
  42,26,"Yakira ubusabe bwa babandi bemeye bakanakora ibikorwa byiza, ndetse akanabongerera mu ngabire ze. Kandi abahakanyi ibihano bikaze. bazahanishwa"
  42,27,"N’iyo Allah aza gutuburira amafunguro abagaragu be, bari kwigomeka ku isi, ariko abamanurira (amafunguro) ku rugero ashatse. Mu by’ukuri, azi kandi abona byimazeyo iby’abagaragu be (bakora)"
  42,28,"Ni na we umanura imvura nyuma y’uko (abantu) biheba, maze agasakaza impuhwe ze. Kandi ni Umurinzi, Ushimwa cyane"
  42,29,"No mu bimenyetso bye, ni iremwa ry’ibirere n’isi ndetse n’inyamaswa yakwirakwijemo. Kandi ashoboye kuzabakoranya igihe azashakira"